  <h2>Get Started</h2>

  <h3>Prerequisites</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <strong>Node.js LTS</strong> - <a href="https://nodejs.org/"
        >Download from nodejs.org</a>
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Git</strong> - <a href="https://git-scm.com/"
        >Download from git-scm.com</a>
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Docker</strong> (optional) - For running local vector databases
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h3>CLI Installation</h3>
  <CodeBlock
    code={`# npm
npx create-ai-stack-starter@latest

# pnpm
pnpm create ai-stack-starter@latest

# bun
bun create ai-stack-starter@latest`}
    lang="bash"
  />

  <p>
    Follow the interactive prompts to choose your architecture, database, auth,
    LLM provider, and add-ons.
  </p>

  <h3>Skip Prompts (Default Stack)</h3>
  <CodeBlock
    code={`npx create-ai-stack-starter@latest my-app --yes`}
    lang="bash"
  />

  <h2>Common Setups</h2>

  <h3>Next.js Fullstack (Recommended)</h3>
  <CodeBlock
    code={`npx create-ai-stack-starter@latest my-app \\
  --architecture nextjs \\
  --database neon \\
  --auth better-auth \\
  --llm openai \\
  --addons tailwind,biome`}
    lang="bash"
  />

  <h3>FastAPI + Next.js (ML Teams)</h3>
  <CodeBlock
    code={`npx create-ai-stack-starter@latest my-app \\
  --architecture fastapi \\
  --database supabase \\
  --auth clerk \\
  --llm anthropic \\
  --vector qdrant`}
    lang="bash"
  />

  <h3>TypeScript Backend (Edge)</h3>
  <CodeBlock
    code={`npx create-ai-stack-starter@latest my-app \\
  --architecture typescript \\
  --backend hono \\
  --database turso \\
  --auth better-auth \\
  --llm openai`}
    lang="bash"
  />

  <h2>Flags Cheat Sheet</h2>
  <p>
    See the full list in the <a href="/docs/cli">CLI Reference</a>. Key flags:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><code>--architecture</code>: nextjs, fastapi, typescript</li>
    <li><code>--database</code>: neon, supabase, turso, sqlite</li>
    <li><code>--auth</code>: better-auth, nextauth, clerk, none</li>
    <li><code>--llm</code>: openai, anthropic, novita, ollama</li>
    <li><code>--vector</code>: qdrant, weaviate, pgvector, pinecone</li>
    <li><code>--addons</code>: tailwind, biome, pwa, analytics</li>
  </ul>

